The masters of anime join forces to create this stunning animated film featuring three separate stories: Magnetic Rose, Stink Bomb and Cannon Fodder.
 In Magnetic Rose, two space travellers are drawn into an asteroid world created by one woman's memories.
 In Stink Bomb, a young lab assistant accidentally transforms himself into a human biological weapon set on a direct course to Tokyo.
 Cannon Fodder depicts a day in the life of a city whose entire purpose is the firing of cannons at the enemy.
